WHY THE DAILY THRIVE
We created The Daily Thrive to bring you together with top wellness experts and equally passionate parents ready to learn, grow, and flourish.

Therapist-designed, mental wellness platform crafted to meet the unique needs of parents. We support parent mental and emotional health with 1:1 chat-based professional coaching, live in-app events, daily fresh expert-crafted wellness content, and a private, facilitated community.

SIX REASONS TO INSTALL Yes Collective:

1. Personal chat-based professional coaching for parent mental & emotional wellness

Yes Collective coaches help parents with expert-designed practices, skills, and tools to reduce stress and anxiety, overcome burnout, learn how to live closer to what truly matters to them, and discover how to show up for themselves and their family in ever more present, connected, and authentic ways.

2. E-learning with expert masterclasses

Yes Collective masterclasses are expert-designed courses focused on the mental and emotional challenges that matter most to parents such as parent + teen relationships, parent self-doubt and self-criticism, emotional authenticity in parenting, embodied stress management, and nutrition, sleep, and activity for optimal family mental wellness.

3. Expert articles, guides, & interviews

Each week we publish fresh expert articles by doctors, psychologists, researchers, and therapists on topics that matter for parent mental and emotional wellness. From the latest research on communication skills that work to how-to guides on breathwork and emotional processing, we have a library full of science + wisdom just for parents.

4. A private social network community

All the Yes Collective awesomeness revolves around a private, facilitated community of parents just like you, looking to thrive amidst the overwhelm and exhaustion of the modern world. Yes Collective helps you connect with other parents who live in your area and care about doing the inner work to show up for their family as their best selves.

5. Live in-app events

Amazing expert-led live events guide parents in evidence-based and real-world-tested practices for reducing stress and anxiety, processing deep emotions, aligning body, heart, and mind, and communicating with grounded authenticity and loving connection.

6. Podcast, AMAs, & summaries

The Yes Collective Podcast, member-only AMAs, and easy-to-use summaries are hosted in the app. You can listen right in the app, chat with other parents, and save the game-changing tools and tips we share from the experts in each episode.

YES COLLECTIVE

Welcome to a new model of mental wellness, just for parents.

We're in the midst of a mental health crisis for parents. Parenting today is hard, and we're here for it.

Yes Collective offers a first-of-its-kind therapist-designed mental wellness platform crafted to meet the unique needs of parents. We support parent mental health with 1:1 chat-based professional coaching, live in-app events, daily fresh expert-crafted wellness content, and a private, facilitated community.

We're all about gently breaking old cycles and building new skills for multi-generational health & well-being. Because parent thriving is an inside job.

YES COACHING

Amazing expert wellness content only works when you have a supportive guide helping you discover what matters most to you and what small steps to take next. Yes Coaching is our groundbreaking mental and emotional wellness program designed specifically for parents.

The Yes Collective coaching approach is grounded in positive psychology, cutting edge mental health therapy models, & health behavior science. Every step of the program is guided by professional health coaches and begins with parents discovering their own natural strengths, recurring patterns, and what matters most to them.

Start your Yes Journey today & join us in the app!
